        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "眼觸自性無所有，耳、鼻、舌、身、意觸自性亦無所有，是菩薩摩訶薩於中不住故名退轉。",
        "from": "T06n0220_325:0662c27_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善現！",
