        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_325:0663a17_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "布施波羅蜜多自性無所有，淨戒、安忍、精進、靜慮、般若波羅蜜多自性亦無所有，是菩薩摩訶薩於中不住故名退轉。",
        "from": "T06n0220_325:0663a17_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
