    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_325:0663a25_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "內空自性無所有，外空乃至無性自性空自性亦無所有，是菩薩摩訶薩於中不住故名退轉。",
        "from": "T06n0220_325:0663a25_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
