    {
        "source_sentence": "善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_325:0663b01_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真如自性無所有，法界乃至不思議界自性亦無所有，是菩薩摩訶薩於中不住故名退轉。",
        "from": "T06n0220_325:0663b01_24",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
